法規內容.條文內容:
The Institute’s operations and functions are stated as following:
1.Execution of the on-the-job training development of senior civil servants of the agencies subordinated to the Executive Yuan and local agencies;
2.Execution of important policies and research on laws & regulations of the Executive Yuan;
3.Execution of personnel training of the agencies subordinated to the Executive Yuan and local agencies;
4.Execution of the civil service e-learning and lifelong learning of the agencies subordinated to the Executive Yuan and local agencies;
5.Planning and execution of the cooperation and exchange with related domestic/foreign training development organizations;
6.Research on management and development of civil service resources;
7.Consultation and guidance of civil service training of the agencies subordinated to the Executive Yuan and local agencies;
8.Other matters related to training and development of civil servants of the agencies subordinated to the Executive Yuan and local agencies.
